    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join our Discord!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366270/extras/8afb924c6a8bca9eb5003e1329726888.poster.avif?t=1755727518\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366270/extras/8afb924c6a8bca9eb5003e1329726888.webm?t=1755727518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366270/extras/8afb924c6a8bca9eb5003e1329726888.mp4?t=1755727518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After touching a mysterious sphere artifact, you're transported to the dimension where Balloo`s Mall vanished. Once you entered the mall, it's now a decaying place haunted by warped, immortal beings. Uncover the artifact that keeps them alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366270/extras/2dd1e169e96f6058c668b45a76c53718.poster.avif?t=1755727518\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366270/extras/2dd1e169e96f6058c668b45a76c53718.webm?t=1755727518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366270/extras/2dd1e169e96f6058c668b45a76c53718.mp4?t=1755727518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>When the Dnipro Research Company discovers sphere-shaped artifacts buried deep in Eastern European caves, contact with them teleport anyone  to other dimension. One such artifact caused the sudden <i>disappearance of Balloo`s Mall</i>, a real-world shopping center that simply vanished — leaving behind only an empty place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are sent in dimension which keeps Balloo`s Mall within. You awaken in a liminal, decaying version of the mall, now suspended in another reality. The people who were once trapped there have changed — assimilated into unkillable forms by a mysterious force that keeps them alive. Somewhere inside, that force still exists… and your mission is to retrieve it.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366270/extras/9c93957f12a6ac64e0736bbba2f15c0b.poster.avif?t=1755727518\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366270/extras/9c93957f12a6ac64e0736bbba2f15c0b.webm?t=1755727518\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366270/extras/9c93957f12a6ac64e0736bbba2f15c0b.mp4?t=1755727518\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Liminal Spaces.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmosphere.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cool lore.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something new.</p></li></ul>",
